name: imaginary journey
description: a journey of imagination in the style of decorative Surrrealism that is full of images. In a landscape of dark and magical places as in dream reality and imaginative creatures, among whom many ideas and desires grow. This painting takes us to the subconscious world with various problems of irony in personal life. This painting leads us to explore the process of creating, looking for an idea and putting it in a visual form.
